        "prompt": "Write 3 sentences comparing life in a city and in the countryside. Use words from today's lesson such as 'public transport', 'cleaner air', or 'quiet environment', and use a comparative (e.g. bigger, quieter, faster).",
        "target_length": "3 sentences (approx. 30-45 words)",
        "focus_skill": "Writing simple present comparisons with comparatives and topic vocabulary.",
        "useful_language": [
